          "text": "<p>A lizardfolk acting this turn sets up a net trap into the area. The first time an enemy steps into a square with a net trap, they make an <strong>Agility test</strong>. If the creature was unaware of the trap, they take a bane on the test.</p><table><tbody><tr><td data-colwidth=\"107\"><p>11 or less</p></td><td><p>Restrained (save ends).</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"107\"><p>12-16</p></td><td><p>Restrained (EoT).</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"107\"><p>17+</p></td><td><p>No Effect.</p></td></tr></tbody></table> <p>Any creature not also restrained by a net trap who is adjacent to a creature restrained by the trap can free them as a maneuver.</p>"
